{"tid":1391324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[今日問真啲]阿叔同你解釋點解兩代人大分歧！","createTime":"2019-07-31T11:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T11:57:33.000Z","uid":141789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"237e9ee6b7246a9e2ff9ff5c39f4603d3a24889b","tid":1391324,"uid":141789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:42:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B0kl9ZWgW59/?igshid=1bjkbmok4jorc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB0kl9ZWgW59%2F%3Figshid%3D1bjkbmok4jorc&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFv%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=58bb22c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB0kl9ZWgW59%2F%3Figshid%3D1bjkbmok4jorc&h=076e1d69\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B0kl9ZWgW59/?igshid=1bjkbmok4jorc</a><br />\n想睇精華就飛去最後條片睇阿叔點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e6b3f0c0f12ce520e3c56f9b927001dcce1a2c","tid":1391324,"uid":141789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:54:29.000Z","msg":"「你覺得點解兩代人會咁大分歧？」<br />\n<br />\n「就好奇怪嘅就話，<br />\n喂以前我哋冇飯食喎中國，而家有飯食喎幾好啊！<br />\n你哋反乜嘢啊？搞亂個社會冇飯食<br />\n我話，豬都有飯食啦，咁豬係咪有人權啊？<br />\n冇嘢講㗎嘛你咁樣講法<br />\n當年六十年代毛澤東年代<br />\n你冇飯食就身處十八層地獄<br />\n但係你而家望到香港係好過當年㗎喇喎<br />\n我哋而家喺十七層地獄喎，我唔係喺十八層地獄喎<br />\n我應該覺得十七層地獄呢個係天堂嚟㗎係咪呀<br />\n點解我哋要反呢？<br />\n問題細路仔睇到呢個係第十七層地獄，<br />\n我哋要真正嘅天堂，我哋唔係要地獄！<br />\n所以大家個分歧真係幾明顯。」"},{"pid":"dc28941a965b3fc08d539bc12c0645be913abd28","tid":1391324,"uid":141789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:55:06.000Z","msg":"8月5號全港罷工！！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/THUoLmj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTHUoLmj.png&h=fe7fc8ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0628f3f274c48b3266843dc58ddfee373c8daaf","tid":1391324,"uid":141789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:5